Package tsp

Interface Summary
HeuristicTSP Interface defining the behavior of a TSP heuristic
 

Class Summary
DecreasingArcHeuristicTSP This heuristic sorts the arcs by increasing value and considers each arc in turn for insertion An arc is inserted if and only if it does not create a subtour.
InsertHeuristicTSP This heuristic iteratively appends a customer to the current solution until a tour is obtained
LowerBoundTSP  
MainTSP  
NodeTSP  
TestTSP Utility class to test algorithms for the TSP.
TSPData TPPData : utilities to load TSPData into a matrix from a TSP instance in the format TSPLIB with euclidian distances Data are stored as doubles.
